<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>前端技术学习</title><link>https://gandli.github.io/</link><description>MemE is a powerful and highly customizable GoHugo theme for personal blogs.</description><generator>Hugo 0.85.0 https://gohugo.io/</generator><language>en</language><managingEditor>chenxuexin@gmail.com (gandli)</managingEditor><webMaster>chenxuexin@gmail.com (gandli)</webMaster><copyright>[CC BY-NC-SA 4.0](https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/deed.en)</copyright><lastBuildDate>Fri, 09 Jul 2021 16:58:31 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" href="https://gandli.github.io/rss.xml"/><item><title>Taro</title><link>https://gandli.github.io/posts/taro/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://gandli.github.io/posts/taro/</guid><pubDate>Thu, 17 Jun 2021 10:16:11 +0800</pubDate><author>chenxuexin@gmail.com (gandli)</author><copyright>[CC BY-NC-SA 4.0](https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/deed.en)</copyright><description>&lt;h1 id="taro">Taro&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>Taro 是一个开放式跨端跨框架解决方案，支持使用 React/Vue/Nerv 等框架来开发微信/京东/百度/支付宝/字节跳动/ QQ 小程序/H5 等应用。现如今市面上端的形态多种多样，Web、React Native、微信小程序等各种端大行其道，当业务要求同时在不同的端都要求有所表现的时候，针对不同的端去编写多套代码的成本显然非常高，这时候只编写一套代码就能够适配到多端的能力就显得极为需要。&lt;/p></description><category domain="https://gandli.github.io/categories/javascrpit/">JavaScrpit</category><category domain="https://gandli.github.io/categories/taro/">Taro</category><category domain="https://gandli.github.io/tags/javascrpit/">JavaScrpit</category><category domain="https://gandli.github.io/tags/taro/">Taro</category></item><item><title>Vue.js</title><link>https://gandli.github.io/posts/vue/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://gandli.github.io/posts/vue/</guid><pubDate>Tue, 15 Jun 2021 20:01:20 +0800</pubDate><author>chenxuexin@gmail.com (gandli)</author><copyright>[CC BY-NC-SA 4.0](https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/deed.en)</copyright><description>&lt;h1 id="vuejshttpsv3cnvuejsorg">&lt;a href="https://v3.cn.vuejs.org/">vue.js&lt;/a>&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>Vue (读音 /vjuː/，类似于 view) 是一套用于构建用户界面的渐进式框架。与其它大型框架不同的是，Vue 被设计为可以自底向上逐层应用。Vue 的核心库只关注视图层，不仅易于上手，还便于与第三方库或既有项目整合。另一方面，当与现代化的工具链以及各种支持类库结合使用时，Vue 也完全能够为复杂的单页应用提供驱动。&lt;/p></description><category domain="https://gandli.github.io/categories/javascrpit/">JavaScrpit</category><category domain="https://gandli.github.io/categories/vue/">Vue</category><category domain="https://gandli.github.io/tags/javascrpit/">JavaScrpit</category><category domain="https://gandli.github.io/tags/vue/">Vue</category></item><item><title>JavaScrpit</title><link>https://gandli.github.io/posts/javascrpit/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://gandli.github.io/posts/javascrpit/</guid><pubDate>Sat, 12 Jun 2021 19:44:22 +0800</pubDate><author>chenxuexin@gmail.com (gandli)</author><copyright>[CC BY-NC-SA 4.0](https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/deed.en)</copyright><description>&lt;h1 id="javascrpithttpsdevelopermozillaorgzh-cndocswebjavascript">&lt;a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript">JavaScrpit&lt;/a>&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>JavaScript ( JS ) 是一种具有函数优先的轻量级，解释型或即时编译型的编程语言。虽然它是作为开发 Web 页面的脚本语言而出名的，但是它也被用到了很多非浏览器环境中，例如 Node.js、 Apache CouchDB 和 Adobe Acrobat。JavaScript 是一种基于原型编程、多范式的动态脚本语言，并且支持面向对象、命令式和声明式（如函数式编程）风格。&lt;/p></description><category domain="https://gandli.github.io/categories/javascrpit/">JavaScrpit</category><category domain="https://gandli.github.io/tags/javascrpit/">JavaScrpit</category></item><item><title>你好，世界</title><link>https://gandli.github.io/posts/hello-world/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://gandli.github.io/posts/hello-world/</guid><pubDate>Sat, 12 Jun 2021 16:21:50 +0800</pubDate><author>chenxuexin@gmail.com (gandli)</author><copyright>[CC BY-NC-SA 4.0](https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/deed.en)</copyright><description>&lt;h1 id="你好世界">你好，世界！&lt;/h1></description><category domain="https://gandli.github.io/categories/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E7%AF%87/">第一篇</category><category domain="https://gandli.github.io/categories/%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD/">你好</category><category domain="https://gandli.github.io/tags/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E7%AF%87/">第一篇</category><category domain="https://gandli.github.io/tags/%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD/">你好</category></item></channel></rss>